{"tid":2372214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃國桐為年輕抗爭者傷感 憶被拘押時向已故雙親說：係時候帶我走","createTime":"2021-01-19T12:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T01:30:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":592,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0832bc2d5e0f62464fa94ea62e3008f0fc6d0f","tid":2372214,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:51:32.000Z","msg":"律師兼民主黨九龍城區議員黃國桐上周四（14日）被指涉嫌協助12港人潛逃而被捕，被扣查超過40小時後獲釋。黃獲保釋後昨午在網台節目《三點維權》現身，提到拘捕過程中令他更了解年青被捕者的恐懼，直言面對目前境況，他在被捕期間向已過身的父母說：「係時候帶我走」，更在節目上淚灑當場。<br />\n<br />\n72歲的黃國桐被捕後如常主持網台節目，坦言對香港的目前情況傷感，直斥「好眼冤」，形容民主派之間都有被捕的陰霾：「係辛苦嘅，唔知幾時（警察）再敲門、幾時再嚟、分分鐘係聽日、分分鐘係一陣間」。他又透露，有被捕者經常夢見自己再次被捕，無法入眠，或者直至凌晨6時後，得知自己沒有被捕後才可入睡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/NP45HMICURD45PABVOS24HSANQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FNP45HMICURD45PABVOS24HSANQ%2F&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmenGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=3e3ee181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FNP45HMICURD45PABVOS24HSANQ%2F&h=3773540a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/NP45HMICURD45PABVOS24HSANQ/</a>"},{"pid":"16cbed7b69f2d386d99b0a6b4fd7e43be01428d3","tid":2372214,"uid":183844,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"留喺到嘅得諗每一刻都會有咁嘅諗法"},{"pid":"6e1b62498afd9124d279f1e5021d5d3b2f35b9b1","tid":2372214,"uid":10637,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"桐叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f93d77090cd9ab1a8288c30e31357d5666a0d18","tid":2372214,"uid":51271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"萬事小心"},{"pid":"14684ed16764873e64731217be1248efe206ca37","tid":2372214,"